31,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bc434c9d7fe98c4d3df6632a90dec4533dd6288","tid":2223931,"uid":368287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f9150adf43524058374e7cf799d874a0312fae8","tid":2223931,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"想知斷食幫唔幫到濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中西醫咩方法試過曬都冇用，得斷食未試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"有用 認真過來人 我用類用到絕望 之後轉斷食戒糖 好好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"戒糖我都長期戒緊，想問下斷食你係點斷架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"其實我試過好多階段 戒糖個陣皮膚一樣會好紅又爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後試過入過院 後尾研究下極端少少既方法 卒之就去到生酮同斷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一方面戒碳水化合物 一方面就18/6 我每次一發個陣<br />\n轉返呢個飲食法就會穩定返<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有食supplement幫助下 你當係醫生費 幾百蚊到<br />\n斷食既話 如果之前食好多碳水 我就長斷食2-3日 。<br />\n等身體消耗曬醣 同埋有自噬作用可以吞噬老舊細胞 <br />\n轉化做蛋白質 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我比佢折磨過幾年 中西醫都睇過 中醫我就無咩感覺<br />\n西醫起碼叫可以幫你睇住個情況 但免疫系統病無得醫<br />\n所以話比錢睇D出名醫生都未必有用"},{"pid":"d0d0bec0000bd7d0e3eb25c163c573f2ac76eae6","tid":2223931,"uid":373724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bffa9ec0a338c1aca846d1d60082fac7a970a3a","tid":2223931,"uid":224044,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"識人斷食一個月，好乾身，過埋身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bf598d31cb898a10afa1c029559988b0ca1fa8","tid":2223931,"uid":167931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}